#: addons/amazons-txa.wad/postload.lua:16 input:16 standard
msgctxt "amazons_worker"
msgid "Burns rare trees to produce charcoal more efficiently."
msgstr "Crema arbres rars per produir carbó vegetal de manera més eficient."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for an Amazon production site: Rare Tree Kiln
#: addons/amazons-txa.wad/postload.lua:26 input:26 standard
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid ""
"‘You think you've mastered the art of burning charcoal. But the best "
"charcoal is that which can only be made from rubber when placed in the "
"hottest fire of ironwood. What you've learnt so far, my girl, is barely "
"enough to start learning how to ignite ironwood. You have to start slowly, "
"with the gentle flames of a balsa fire…’"
msgstr ""
"\"Creus que has dominat l'art de cremar carbó vegetal. Però el millor carbó "
"vegetal és el que només es pot fer amb cautxú quan es col·loca al foc més "
"calent de la fusta de ferro. El que has après fins ara, nena, amb prou "
"feines és suficient per començar a aprendre a encendre fusta de ferro. Has "
"de començar a poc a poc, amb les suaus flames d'un foc de balsa...'"

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for an Amazon production site: Rare Tree Kiln
#: addons/amazons-txa.wad/postload.lua:28 input:28 standard
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid "Mistress Blackwood, teaching an apprentice"
msgstr "Mistress Blackwood, ensenyant a un aprenent"

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Amazon production site: Rare Tree Kiln
#: addons/amazons-txa.wad/postload.lua:30 input:30 standard
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid "Burns rare trees into charcoal."
msgstr "Crema arbres rars en carbó vegetal."

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for an Amazon production site: Rare Tree Kiln
#: addons/amazons-txa.wad/postload.lua:32 input:32 standard
#, lua-format
msgctxt "amazons_building"
msgid ""
"If fully supplied, the rare tree kiln needs %s on average to produce one "
"lump of coal."
msgstr ""
"Si està totalment subministrat, el forn d'arbres rars necessita %s de "
"mitjana per produir un tros de carbó."

